    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>体验陆地与海洋交汇的战争。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<i>Men of War: Red Tide</i>》将即时战略的战术深度与第三人称直接作战的原始冲击力融合在一起。本独立资料片由作家兼概念作者亚历山大·佐里奇参与创作，讲述了“黑衣军”——苏联海军陆战队的故事，这支精英部队在二战黑海战役中因其冷酷精准而声名远扬。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130/extras/61bd85828dad8e4068faa1950ea8182d.poster.avif?t=1771000141\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130/extras/61bd85828dad8e4068faa1950ea8182d.webm?t=1771000141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130/extras/61bd85828dad8e4068faa1950ea8182d.mp4?t=1771000141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带领你的部队完成23个任务，再现东线战场上最激烈的战斗——从敖德萨和塞瓦斯托波尔到尼古拉耶夫和康斯坦察。协调两栖进攻、夺取敌军防御工事，指挥装甲列车、海军舰队和航空兵，在混乱的战火中杀出一条生路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130/extras/923b19810bde85adeef5fe029aa527f2.poster.avif?t=1771000141\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130/extras/923b19810bde85adeef5fe029aa527f2.webm?t=1771000141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130/extras/923b19810bde85adeef5fe029aa527f2.mp4?t=1771000141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<i>Men of War: Red Tide</i>》提供真实的氛围、具有挑战性的任务，以及大规模战术与直接控制的完美结合。战役内容丰富且具有历史深度，将大规模行动与紧张的近距离英雄主义融合在一起——这正是《<i>Men of War</i>》体验的核心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130/extras/6fcdc8656989ea97cf6b9c2bf6db7718.poster.avif?t=1771000141\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130/extras/6fcdc8656989ea97cf6b9c2bf6db7718.webm?t=1771000141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130/extras/6fcdc8656989ea97cf6b9c2bf6db7718.mp4?t=1771000141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >功能</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>大型单人剧情战役</strong>——包含20多个精心打造的任务，覆盖1941至1945年间六大战略行动。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>四个可操作阵营</strong>——在多样化的战场上指挥苏联、德国、罗马尼亚和意大利部队。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超过100种真实军事单位</strong>——包括坦克、火炮、自行火炮、装甲车、军舰和飞机。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>直接控制系统</strong>——随时直接操控任意士兵或载具，在战略视角和近距离战斗间无缝切换。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>海军与空军支援</strong>——部署巡洋舰、驱逐舰、鱼雷艇、轰炸机和水上飞机，扭转战局。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>电影级战场沉浸感</strong>——动态天气、可破坏环境和真实伤害模型让每一场战斗都栩栩如生。</p></li></ul>",
